"NAME                                      \n"
"    expresstest - works with express test subsystem     \n"
"SYNOPSIS                                  \n"
"    expresstest [-h] [-n <test_num> [-i]] \n"
"DESCRIPTION                               \n"
"    shows available express tests and     \n"
"    executes test if specified            \n"
"OPTIONS                                   \n"
"    -n TESTNUM -  set test number        \n"
"    -i -  show test info                 \n"
"                                          \n"
"  if nothing specified, shows list of     \n"
"  available express tests                 \n"
